::heading level=1 id=virtual-check
Virtual Filesystem Check
::end

::paragraph id=virtual-check-summary
Virtual doc paths should hydrate from SQLite-backed state and remain consistent with source serialization.
::end

::code id=virtual-check-table language=html
<table>
	<thead><tr><th>Path</th><th>Expectation</th><th>Status</th></tr></thead>
	<tbody>
		<tr><td>docdb:/examples/welcome.dx</td><td>Loads typed block source</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
		<tr><td>docdb:/examples/tutorial.dx</td><td>Renders html table and svg</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
		<tr><td>docdb:/documents/compact-proof.dx</td><td>Metrics JSON preserved</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
		<tr><td>docdb:/documents/final-validation.dx</td><td>Dashboard view capture succeeds</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
	</tbody>
</table>
::end

